Initial v0.1.0
- Initial release of ProgressTODO
- Added support for Checkbox, Bar, and nested List todos
- Added weights for todos to affect progress
- Added countdown timers for tasks with start/end dates
- Added Starring, Urgent, and Archiving of todos
- Added localStorage persistence
- Added Copy and Paste of todos as JSON
- Added basic modals for About, Starred, and Urgent
- Implemented minimal clean UI

Update v0.2.0
- Added Drag abd Drop
- Added a Battle Pass
- Added Hiding and Showing Done ToDos with continuous support for Archiving them
- Imporved UI Design
- Fixed issues with Scroll To Top
- ESC key closes all menus and models globally
- Moved app state to pinia powered storage
- Changed the copied data from JSON to CSV, cutting the size of average todolist in half!
- FIX: made all components use the same [ name / label / text ]



